OL,3,CWales' pothole crisis dubbed 'the
OL,4,Cworst nightmare ever' for drivers
OL,6,FWales' ongoing pothole crisis has been
OL,7,Fdescribed by motorists in Newport as a
OL,8,F"nightmare," causing thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds in vehicle damage.
OL,11,FThis year alone, the AA said it has
OL,12,Fbeen been called out to more than
OL,13,F4,600 pothole-related breakdowns - a
OL,14,Ffigure up 14% compared to January and
OL,15,FFebruary last year.
OL,17,FThe increase is being put down to
OL,18,Frecord rainfall impacting the
OL,19,Fcondition of our roads.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
