OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1772708726
OL,3,CWales' pothole crisis dubbed 'the
OL,4,Cworst nightmare ever' for drivers
OL,6,FMatthew decided to take action against
OL,7,FNewport Council and successfully
OL,8,Fsettled out of court for #2,500.
OL,10,FA Freedom of Information request
OL,11,Frevealed that in the past three years,
OL,12,FNewport Council received 174 pothole
OL,13,Fdamage claims and has paid out nearly
OL,14,F#25,000 in compensation.
OL,16,FLocals in the area described the
OL,17,Fsituation as "the worst nightmare ever
OL,18,Fin Newport".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
