OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1772708726
OL,3,CWales' pothole crisis dubbed 'the
OL,4,Cworst nightmare ever' for drivers
OL,6,FIn response, Councillor Rhian Howells
OL,7,Fsaid: "I wouldn't want any resident to
OL,8,Ffeel like they need to be jumping to
OL,9,Favoid potholes.
OL,11,F"We have heard him (Matthew); we have
OL,12,Fheard other residents. I get contacted
OL,13,Fdaily about potholes and we have
OL,14,Fheard. Part of it was simply that we
OL,15,Fneeded the money to do it.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
