OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1772708726
OL,3,CWales' pothole crisis dubbed 'the
OL,4,Cworst nightmare ever' for drivers
OL,6,F"We have the money to do it (now) and,
OL,7,Fas you can see, we have absolutely
OL,8,Fprioritised the roads in the last
OL,9,Fbudget, and even more so in this
OL,10,Fbudget. It's a huge investment and
OL,11,Fpeople are really going to see the
OL,12,Fdifference."
OL,14,FIn February 2026, the Welsh Government
OL,15,Fannounced that its local government
OL,16,Fborrowing scheme had enabled councils
OL,17,Fto fix or prevent around 171,000
OL,18,Fpotholes across 324 miles of local
OL,19,Froads in Wales since April 2025.
OL,26,@nD@]pmnD@apn
