OL,3,CWales' pothole crisis dubbed 'the
OL,4,Cworst nightmare ever' for drivers
OL,6,FTransport secretary Ken Skates
OL,7,Fpreviously said: "Fixing our roads is
OL,8,Fa priority for this government.
OL,10,F"We have significantly increased our
OL,11,Finvestment in road maintenance and
OL,12,Fpreventative treatments this financial
OL,13,Fyear to deliver improvements across
OL,14,Fboth the strategic and local road
OL,15,Fnetworks.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
